hoofandM;LAN operating systems should do things for you, not to you.andP;  LANtastic, fromArtisoft, is the smallest, fastest, kindest LAN operating system, with thetightest code we've yet seen.andP;  For a shade over $200 per station, LANtasticdelivers electronic mail, well-designed menus, and serious network-managementand security-management tools.andP;  LANtastic is technically excellent networkingsoftware.andO;</TEXT></DOC>